{
  "stem": "7546.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 1944, in July, one of the important factories in the ghetto all of a sudden closed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they started taking out the machinery, fabric, and even unfinished work was taken-- taken out from that factory, carted onto trucks, and taken out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a very bad sign.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the sign was that something is going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Since they picked on their first factory, an important factory in the ghetto, that made uniforms for women in the German army, is being closed, God knows which factory is going to be closed next.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we knew something was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We also knew that the Warsaw ghetto had a uprising.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Warsaw ghetto is no more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Therefore, we were afraid, what is actually going on, that they really picked on this factory to be closed?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we started hearing rumors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you actually been fed rumors since the first day of the war-- we were fed rumors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then another factory was closed, a men's factory was closed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we walked out in the morning and we saw a sign, which was hung out-- every couple of days we had a sign on the walls to read.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is happening, or the rations are changed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This case was to the inhabitants of ghetto Lodz-- the ghetto is being resettled to a different part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every able man, woman, and child that is able to work and contribute to the betterment of the German land, and help the German army that is fighting a successful war against the Americans, and against the English, and against the Russians, will be resettled into a different part of Germany, and work, and be fed, and be clothed-- and not to worry about the future.",
      "word_count": 67
    }
  ],
